hen adding the spices.","Sugar can be replaced with maple syrup. Bake for an additional 10 minutes when using maple syrup.","Replace almonds with another nut of your choice or use 21 oz of unsalted mixed nuts e.g. 7 oz pecans, 7 oz walnuts and 7 oz almonds.","To make your own Chinese five spice: place 6 star anise, 0.5 oz Sichuan pepper, 0.5 oz fennel seeds, 2 tbsp whole cloves and 1 cinnamon stick into mixing bowl and grind <strong>1 min\/speed 10<\/strong>. Scrape down sides of mixing bowl with spatula and mix a further <b><strong>30 sec\/speed 10<\/strong><b>. Store in an airtight container until needed.","Divide nuts into festive jars for gifting."],"basicInfo":["easy","10m","1h 40m","13 portions"]}